<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />The angel of Yahweh camps around those who fear him</para>

<para style="q1">and rescues them.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />Taste and see that Yahweh is good.</para>

<para style="q1">Blessed is the man who takes refuge in him.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />Fear Yahweh, you his holy people.</para>

<para style="q1">There is no lack for those who fear him.</para>
